as we swung past Buckingham Palace

878
00:58:34,185 --> 00:58:35,905
这感觉变得更加特殊
and onto The Mall.

879
00:58:40,185 --> 00:58:42,305
这比我想象的还要多
There's more than I thought.

880
00:58:57,905 --> 00:59:02,584
林荫大道这些年举办过很多庆典
The Mall has hosted many uplifting scenes over the years.

881
00:59:02,585 --> 00:59:07,184
但是这里从没举办过这样的聚会
But it has never hosted anything quite like this before.

882
00:59:07,185 --> 00:59:11,384
让我们惊叹不已的不仅是这壮观的场面
It wasn't just the sheer volume that took our breath away.

883
00:59:11,385 --> 00:59:14,425
更是这些种类繁多的差异性，这种宽宏的气势
It was the diversity, the breadth.

884
00:59:16,785 --> 00:59:20,784
轿车，卡车，挖掘机，赛车
Cars, lorries, diggers, racers,

885
00:59:20,785 --> 00:59:23,344
冰淇凌车，灵车
ice cream vans, hearses.

886
00:59:23,345 --> 00:59:25,704
真是太壮观了
It was magnificent.

887
00:59:25,705 --> 00:59:27,585
真是大手笔
It was huge.

888
00:59:33,625 --> 00:59:36,024
我都不知道我们制造了这些自卸卡车
I didn't know we made those massive tipper trucks.

889
00:59:36,025 --> 00:59:37,344
看看那车！
Look at that that thing!

890
00:59:37,345 --> 00:59:40,384
拖拉机
A tractor.

891
00:59:40,385 --> 00:59:41,585
完全没想到
I didn't think of that.

892
00:59:44,745 --> 00:59:47,025
陆地最快纪录车！
Land speed record cars!

893
00:59:48,585 --> 00:59:51,865
那是我测评过的巴士！看见了吗，伙计们？
There's my bus! All right, mate?

894
00:59:57,545 --> 00:59:58,585
哦嚯，捷豹鹰E型！
Ooh, the Eagle!

895
01:00:15,705 --> 01:00:17,044
如今很多人这么说
A lot of people say that, today,

896
01:00:17,045 --> 01:00:22,344
英国不过是一个世界银行，或者一个精品商店，或者一个已经没落的昔日霸主
Britain is nothing more than a bank,or a boutique, or a busted flush,

897
01:00:22,345 --> 01:00:27,905
但是看看我身后停着的这些令人惊叹的展示车...
but looking at that staggering collection back there...

898
01:00:28,945 --> 01:00:30,825
我对他们的言论表示怀疑。
I'm not sure they're right.

899
